show.title: Kiss and Switch The Cursed Vampire

हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Daphne is betrayed by her fiancé, who sacrifices her to save his ex-lover from a vampire king. She dies on the altar—but is reborn as a vampire’s eternal companion. When Paul learns of her fate, guilt drives him into madness.
